{"word":"G2343 - θησαυρίζω - thēsaurízō - thay-sow-rid'-zo - Lay up","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θησαυρίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">thēsaurízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">thay-sow-rid'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Lay up</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சேர்த்துவை, வை, குவி"},{"paragraph":"to gather and lay up, to heap up, store up: to accumulate riches"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2344 - θησαυρός - thēsaurós - thay-sow-ros'/2344\">G2344</a>; to <i>amass</i> or <i>reserve</i> (literally or figuratively): - lay up (treasure), (keep) in store, (heap) treasure (together, up).</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2343/2343\">G2343</a>, <a href=\"#/G2344/2344\">G2344</a>"}]}